(472, 'Akihiko Nakagawa', 'anakagawa@strapack.com', '3609515794', 'Strapack, Inc.', 'Packexpo2023', 'Union City', NULL, NULL, '', 'We are looking for 2 sets of clear cages that will be used in Packexpo 2023. \r\nCan you quote the cages?\r\n\r\nRequirements for spec.  Each cage set will enclose the following space.\r\n\r\n1.	W13’xL7’xH7’\r\n2.	W14’xL7’xH7’\r\n \r\nThe reason why We wanted the 2 clear cages for 2 brand new products with new technology.\r\n1.	Nobody should see the inside of the machine. (Except for some people who are allowed such as our sales reps and good business partners) * That’s why it has to be accessible.\r\n2.	We want to keep some distance between the visitors and products so that they can see the operation clearly but they cannot check the details. Also, it can prevent from taking good photos or movies in detail.\r\n3.	Meanwhile, it should look good since it is a show. Not a fence but a clear wall would be nicer.\r\n \r\nOther requirements\r\n1.	Need a door with a lock. As mentioned, some people have to reach the machine for maintenance. Also, we need an operator inside of the cage during the show.\r\n2.	Concerned about the people who get in the cages at night.\r\n3.	Easy to carry and install-> We are going to convey every product from our office in San Francisco to Las Vegas by truck by ourselves including installation. We would have to deliver it without crates because we do not have space to keep the empty crate during the show. So, bringing this cage set from the truck to our booth, the people from the union would take care of it. We are concerned that they cannot move the cages without the damage. The casters might be a good option. If these requirements are hard, installation from your company is also an option.\r\n4.	We are not sure if we use this again in the next show. The rental might be an option.\r\n \r\n\r\n\r\nThis requirement could lead us over our budget. We could compromise some of them. If you have other ideas, it is always appreciated.', '/pack-expo/', '2023-06-21 10:55:03', '2023-06-21 10:55:03', NULL),
