(700, 'Gersende CHEYLAN', 'FUNFORGE', 'gersende@funforge.fr', '+33143700853‬', 'Spiel fair', 'Essen', '150', '15000', '1', 'Hello\r\nFunforge is a french board game publishers and we use to have a booth at the Spiel fair of Essen in Germany, in october. We\'re looking for a new booth constructor partner for this year. Please make us a quotation.\r\nI give you booth simulation, plan of hall 5 and an example for the shelves we need.\r\nWe will have an island stand of 150 msq (10x15m) in hall 5 (stand 1D116 in red on the plan).\r\nWe would like to have :\r\n• 3 offices and 1 storage (3x3m each) with lock. I have indicated the placement of the doors in the scheme.\r\n• a large sales area with a counter and shelves about 2 meters high, with a space of 40 cm between each level (in yello in our scheme). We prefere to have them in wood instead of metal or plastic. They need to be strong enough to put a lot of board games on them (see shelves example picture).\r\n• a long counter (in blue in our scheme) of 6 meters long with shelves underneath and a \"return\" next to the storage door to prevent anybody to come behind it. I think it takes 1 meter between the counter and the shelves so that you can move around behind it.\r\n• full stickers on the 3 walls left.\r\n• Suspension : 3x3m or 4x 4m with our logo in full, on each side.\r\n• lamps (warm color not cold) above the walls to illuminate the tables and the counter\r\n\r\nThis remains 4.5m on each side of the office/storage for the gaming tables.\r\n\r\nMaterials we need:\r\n• 17 white tables of 120x80cm\r\n• 2 white tables of 1.5 x 1.5m\r\n• 4 white standing tables. Do you have any printable fabric solutions (with logo or game name) to put on them? What will be the prize ?)\r\n• 92 white chairs without armrests\r\n• 4 high white stools without backrest\r\n• 4 little fridges (to put in each office and the reserve)\r\n• coat racks in each office and reserve.\r\n• orange carpet\r\n\r\nWe will also have a storage booth (5G122 in blue) where a door with lock should be installed.\r\n\r\nOur budget is 15,000 euros.\r\nIf you have others propositions for us please don\'t hesitate to give us. We looking for something different as we used to do.\r\n\r\nLet me know if you need more pictures or informations.\r\nBest regards', '/stand-design-and-booth-construction-company/essen/', '2023-08-02 21:34:21', '2023-08-02 21:34:21', '92.170.225.152'),
