(728, 'Rushit Doshi', 'Rushit Enterprises', 'info@rushit.in', '9820707156', 'JIS FALL 2023', 'Miami', '10x10', '2000usd', '', 'Hello,\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nI hope this message finds you well. I am writing to discuss the requirements for a custom booth design for our upcoming event. We are excited to explore new ideas and create an engaging and visually appealing booth that highlights our main product, SIEVES.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nBased on our needs, here is a brief summary of our requirements:\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n1. **Flooring:** We are interested in a 4-inch raised wooden flooring for our booth. This will add an elegant touch and provide a distinct visual element.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n2. **Walls and Storage Units:** Our preference is for a 2-sided booth design with wooden matte finish walls. Additionally, we envision incorporating storage units with glass displays to showcase our products. We are open to creative suggestions regarding color, finish, and design for the walls and storage units.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n3. **Graphic Display:** Typically, we display a graphic poster above the storage unit to give customers a visual representation of our products. We are keen to explore innovative display ideas that could enhance the customer experience. If you or your team has any creative concepts, we would be excited to hear them.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n4. **Seating:** As shown in the attached booth picture, we would like a round bar table and three bar stool chairs. However, we are open to alternative seating suggestions that align with the overall booth design and aesthetic.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nWe are particularly interested in ways to emphasize our main product, SIEVES, within the booth design. Any creative ideas you can provide to draw attention to this product would be greatly appreciated.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nAdditionally, we would like to inquire about the possibility and cost of creating a wooden booth similar to the BLACK Color Booth photo attached. This will help us explore different design options and make an informed decision.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nWe greatly value your expertise and input and look forward to collaborating with you to create a booth design that effectively represents our brand and products. Please provide us with your insights, suggestions, and cost estimates at your earliest convenience.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nThank you for your time and assistance.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nBest regards,\r\nRushit Doshi', '/stand-design-and-booth-construction-company/miami/', '2023-08-11 12:13:15', '2023-08-11 12:13:15', '49.36.11.33'),
