(958, 'Mina Hanna', 'Nivex Farms', 'info@nivexfarms.com', '00201063189632', 'Fruit Logistica Berlin 2024', 'Berlin', '28', NULL, '1', 'We are pleased to inform you that we will be participating in Fruit Logistica Berlin 2024. As we prepare for this significant event, we are in need of your services for the design and construction of our stand. The stand we require is a corner stand, covering an area of 28 square meters.\r\n\r\nAllow me to provide a brief overview of our company. We are Egyptian fruit and vegetable growers and exporters, specializing in a range of products including Green Beans, spring onions, strawberries, grapes, and peas. Our commitment to quality and excellence has earned us a strong reputation in the industry.\r\n\r\nGiven our Egyptian heritage, we would prefer the theme of the stand to reflect the pharaonic style, celebrating the rich cultural heritage of our country.\r\n\r\nTo aid in our decision-making process, we kindly request that you provide us with your catalogue or brochure detailing the services you offer, along with estimated costs. This information will assist us in making an informed choice regarding our exhibition stand.\r\n\r\nWe appreciate your prompt attention to this matter and look forward to reviewing your materials', '/fruit-logistica/', '2023-10-02 15:35:53', '2023-10-02 15:35:53', '45.246.204.47'),
