(1224, 'Margarita Shilova', 'Trackunit', 'msh@trackunit.com', '42323010', 'Intermat', 'Aalborg', '57', '27000 eur', '1', 'Hello, we\'re in search of a partner to help us create and build an exhibition stand for INTERMAT in Paris, scheduled for April 24-27. Our stand measures 57 sqm with a one-side wall (9 x 6.5 m), and key elements we require include a 2 sqm storage room/corner, 2 demo stations with tv screens, a bar counter, and an open meeting area. Our estimated budget - 27.000 EUR. We\'d love to connect and delve deeper into the details of this project. Looking forward to discussing this further with you.', '/custom-exhibition-stands/', '2023-12-04 18:44:37', '2023-12-04 18:44:37', '212.112.148.103'),
(1225, 'Paul Pullan', 'Dar Engineering', 'paul.pullan@dar-engineering.com', '00966567972968', 'MIPIM 2024', 'Cannes', '15', 'Negotiable', '1', 'Hi There,\r\nI hope you are doing well. My company, Dar Engineering is attending MIPIM for the first time in March 2024.\r\n\r\nWe are taking a 15 sqm space (P-1.J55) in Zone 4 of Palais -1.  I’ve attached a map for your perusal.\r\n\r\nI’m reaching out to see if I can obtain a quotation for stand design and build for the event. \r\n\r\nWe are really looking at the stand as a networking area, mainly for comfortable space for meetings with customers whilst having ambient project imagery. As a construction consultant this would be largely around our work on developments such as hospitals, hotels, mixed-use developments, entertainment complexes etc. \r\n\r\nWhilst we would want to show our work via wall installations or AV presentation, the focus would be to create an comfortable space to enjoy. I’d also suggest that we have a welcome/coffee networking desk space for informal discussions as well as a more fixed seating areas.\r\nBasically, I want to avoid the stand looking too out-of-the-box and ensure it’s comfortable to manage and meet.\r\nDo let me know if you need any further information from me to begin the process of moving our conversation forward.\r\n\r\nI look forward to hearing from you.\r\n\r\nThanks,\r\n\r\nPaul', '/mipim/', '2023-12-04 18:55:38', '2023-12-04 18:55:38', '37.99.144.254'),
