(1290, 'Lombard', 'EAS Change systems', 'ophelie.lombard@easchangesystems.com', '00000', 'NPE2024', 'Orlando', '400', '15 000', '2', 'Good morning,\r\nI am Ophélie, in charge of marketing for the company EAS Mold & Die Change Systems, Inc. .\r\nI am looking for a booth builder for our 20x20ft booth at the NPE 2024 exhibition. My colleague Thierry Pastor forwarded me your contact.\r\nI will need from you a quotation concerning our project, before organizing a call to discuss it.\r\nWhat we would need from your company is :\r\n- 1 customized backwall of 20ft long and 10ft height with our company color, logo, product image and 1 tv on each side of the wall.\r\n- 1 closet of 6x6 ft, with sink (and water access), coffee machine and storage rack for marketing material and personal belonging)\r\n- floor carpeting\r\n- hanging banner upper our booth.\r\nCan you let me know a rough quotation for me to discuss with our CEO?\r\nNOTE : attached you can find example of the kind of booth backwall, closet and hanging banner we would like.', '/stand-design-and-booth-construction-company/orlando/', '2023-12-07 18:16:22', '2023-12-07 18:16:22', '185.195.249.78'),
