(1298, 'Emma Reno', 'Latitude Aero', 'emma@latitude-aero.com', '8888822929', 'AIX', 'Greensboro', '60', '75.000,00', '2', 'Latitude is currently in the process of preparing for AIX 2024 and is in the market for a potential new stand designer. We are seeking a quotation and design for both a two-story and a one-story stand this year. Our goal is to assess the cost variance between the two options. As we would like to see the cost difference between the two. The maximum we would like to spend is €75.000,00.\r\n \r\nStand number is 5E21\r\nSize: 7.50m x 8m 60.00 m2\r\nOur envisioned layout includes a conference room on the ground floor, complemented by a bar area suitable for serving drinks or coffee. On the second floor, we plan to establish a lounge and meeting area. Additionally, we would require a dedicated storage space for our belongings, including bags, tradeshow giveaways, and food items. As part of our design considerations, we are planning on including 3-6 assemblies of seats and potentially a sidewall display, As well as a front desk area so that we can greet customers and display our tradeshow giveaways.\r\n\r\nWe really like the “wood” floor look and would like to include some color in this year’s design as last year we only did gray and white for our colors. I am attaching a picture of our booth Last year for your reference. I am also attaching two photos that I really like some aspects of. I love the wood & black combination with the led lighting. It feels very modern.\r\n\r\nThank you and we look forward to your response', '/stand-design-and-booth-construction-company/hamburg/', '2023-12-11 20:00:02', '2023-12-11 20:00:02', '107.208.172.90'),
(1299, 'Viktoriia Burmistr', 'Caromed Italia', 'communication@caromed.it', '00393516066452', 'IMCAS World Congress 2024 Paris', NULL, '22.5SQMT', NULL, '1', 'There are some details regarding our booth:\r\n\r\nBooth number: C102\r\n\r\n    3 sides open\r\n    Level 1\r\n    Hall Ternes\r\n    22,5 sqmt\r\n\r\n\r\nThere are some minimum requirements:\r\n\r\n    shelves/podiums for product presentation, maybe with lights\r\n    panels (to put some graphics)\r\n    storage room\r\n    TV and electrical supply\r\n    front desk with logo\r\n    furniture (a small table and couches)\r\n    area bar\r\n    floor\r\n    hight around 3 m', '/contact-us/', '2023-12-11 21:17:32', '2023-12-11 21:17:32', '93.34.91.231'),
