(1818, 'Emily Jones', 'Wilfred Frierson', 'emilyjones2250@gmail.com', '9724956030', 'Emily Jones', NULL, 'SQMT', NULL, '', 'Hi there,\r\n\r\nWe run a YouTube growth service, which increases your number of subscribers both safely and practically. \r\n\r\n- We guarantee to gain you 700-1500+ subscribers per month.\r\n- People subscribe because they are interested in your channel/videos, increasing likes, comments and interaction.\r\n- All actions are made manually by our team. We do not use any \'bots\'.\r\n\r\nThe price is just $60 (USD) per month, and we can start immediately.\r\n\r\nIf you have any questions, let me know, and we can discuss further.\r\n\r\nKind Regards,\r\nEmily', '/contact-us/', '2024-03-16 05:53:37', '2024-03-16 05:53:37', '196.240.104.24'),
(1819, 'Priyesh', 'Industrial filters and Fabrics India', 'priyesh.gawade@iffgroup.com', '+917400530301', 'Filtech 2024', 'Cologne', '54 sq m (9x6)', 'Not decided , depends on idea', '1', 'Dear Sir\r\nWe are Industrial Filters and Fabrics Pvt. Ltd. India participating in Filtech 2024 at Booth no. B21\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nPlease note below details:\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n1) We require Stand Building and Stand Dismantling service.\r\n\r\n2) Attached a basic design idea from our side, to display our Felt roll samples in Stand\r\n\r\n3) Our Stand size is 9x6 (54 Sq Meter). with 3 sides Open.\r\n\r\n4) We require a dedicated Covered conference area in our Booth for private meetings. (shown in Picture)\r\n\r\n5) A small space dedicated for Storage near the Conference area. (shown in Picture)\r\n\r\n6) Rigging from the ceiling in Square / Circular on Max allowed Height with our Logo.\r\n\r\n7) Shelves for display of our FIlter bags , Cages and other samples.\r\n\r\n8) TV unit to be installed for displaying our Company Video.\r\nPlease share the best possible design ideas  and Quote from your side so that we can finalize soon.', '/custom-exhibition-stands/', '2024-03-16 16:33:21', '2024-03-16 16:33:21', '103.9.13.142'),
