(1821, 'Hazel Venida', 'UnaFinancial', 'h.venida@unamarket.ph', '639266163985', 'Dubai Fintech Summit 2024', NULL, 'SQMT', NULL, '', 'Hi there! My name is Hazel Venida, Strategic Communications Manager at UnaFinancial. \r\n\r\nWe are participating in this year\'s Dubai Fintech Summit, and will occupy a 9 sqm. booth in the exhibition.\r\n\r\nIn line with this, I am looking for potential booth suppliers that could construct booths that may be reused and is not just a one-time set-up.\r\n\r\nWe are looking at the following services in particular:\r\n- booth design\r\n- booth construction\r\n- booth transportation to the venue, and to our warehouse after egress\r\n\r\nI hope you could provide me with a response by tomorrow, March 18. Thank you very much.\r\n\r\nYou may reach out to me via h.venida@unamarket.ph.', '/contact-us/', '2024-03-17 22:15:50', '2024-03-17 22:15:50', '112.200.206.230'),
