(1830, 'Gina Annan', 'Entrust', 'gina.annan@entrust.com', '447817667501', 'RSA', 'San Francisco', '20 x 30', 'tbc', '', 'Hi,\r\nI wonder if you could advise what your published rates are for labor. The current company we use seems to be rather costly so i am exploring our options for future events. The labor part of the quote is the only bit I think we are being over charged on.\r\nHere is the description of costs, could you please advise what you would quote for these services.\r\nInstallation and Dismantle - Budgetary Guideline \r\n Description: Includes the following Managed Services: Installation and Dismantle Labor\r\nInstallation: (4) workers on Thur., May 2nd from 1pm - 5pm\r\n(4) workers on Fri., May 3rd from 8am - 5pm\r\n(4) workers on Sat., May 4th from 8am - 5pm\r\n(4) workers on Sun., May 5th from 8am - 5pm\r\n(1) worker on Mon., May 6th from 8am - 5pm\r\nMaintenance: (1) worker May 7-9th from 8am - 10am each day of show\r\nDismantle: (4) workers on Thur., May 9th from 2pm - 10pm\r\n(4) workers on Fr., May 11th from 8am - 5pm\r\nLabor hours are determined by jurisdiction which can vary from venue to venue.\r\nOvertime will be calculated for all labor on weekdays after 4:30PM and Saturdays.\r\nDouble time will be calculated for all labor on Sundays and Holidays.', '/stand-design-and-booth-construction-company/san-francisco/', '2024-03-20 14:52:21', '2024-03-20 14:52:21', '86.129.154.136'),
