(1832, 'Chancie Sibley', 'LoRa Alliance', 'chancie.sibley@lora-alliance.com', '2222222222', 'ACE24', 'Anaheim, CA, USA', '10x30', '25,000', '1', 'I am reaching out for a turnkey, affordable exhibition solution for the ACE24 event at the Anaheim Convention Center on June 11 – 13, 2024. We typically hire through the show provider, Freeman, but I’d like to see if we can find another company to support and be more hands-on with our setup and dismantle as we have limited staff availability from our side during the event.  \r\n\r\nThe LoRa Alliance has a 10x30 ft booth at ACE24, booth 1101, and we have 5 members of our technology Alliance who present in the booth alongside us. Attached is a photo from a previous event of how we’ve set this up and how we brand each individual member “demo counter”. \r\n\r\nRequirements:\r\n•            5 counters with storage and lockable cabinet (each will need power which can be ordered through show management if needed)\r\n•            Each cabinet has branded graphic mounted to the front\r\n•            1 stool per counter\r\n•            Flooring or Carpet (standard, no padding)\r\n•            10x30 backwall graphic with frame / lights\r\n•            1 literature rack\r\n•            1 pop up banner\r\n\r\nBudget: around $25,000\r\n\r\nIs this a booth that fits with your exhibit solutions, and is this an event where you are already have other clients exhibiting?', '/stand-design-and-booth-construction-company/anaheim/', '2024-03-21 08:19:15', '2024-03-21 08:19:15', '35.151.180.27'),
