(1841, 'Iván García', 'Hidramar Group', 'ivan.garcia@hidramar.com', 'xxx xxx xxx', 'SMM Hamburg 2024', 'Hamburg', '15sqm', NULL, '2', 'Dear Sir/Madam,\r\nThis September we are going to participate in the SMM Hamburg Exhibition 2024, and we would need the construction of our stand.\r\nIt is a 15sqm stand, and 2-side open, so we would need a shell scheme with 2 walls, also carpeting, light points, plugs, furniture (2 or 3 chairs and a table), storage space (not too wide) and wallpaping of the two walls. Right now we don\'t have a design for it yet.\r\nThe measures (length and height permitted) are attached.\r\nWe look forward to receive your offer, thank you,\r\nIván G.', '/stand-design-and-booth-construction-company/hamburg/', '2024-03-22 21:05:09', '2024-03-22 21:05:09', '83.59.176.60'),
(1842, 'Sindy Wong', 'Comasia Ltd', 'sindy.wong@comasia.com.hk', '85227006801', 'Asian Christmas, Toys, Gifts & Apparel Expo', 'Dusseldorf', NULL, NULL, '1', 'Dear sir, \r\nGreetings from Hong Kong, we are an event organizer and will hold a Asian Product Expo in Feb 2025 in Messe Dusseldorf where have around 550 x 9sqm booths.  We are pleased to request a quotation from your company for managing the set up & dismantle of our basic booth package as attached.  We schedule Day 1 for booth set up, Day 2 for exhibitor move-in, Day 3-5 show period and Day 5 evening till Day 6 for booth dismantle.\r\nShould your require any further information, please feel free to contact us at any time.  Look forward to receiving your cost proposal by 2 Apr 2024.\r\nRegards\r\nSindy Wong', '/modular-exhibition-stands/', '2024-03-25 10:16:30', '2024-03-25 10:16:30', '223.197.175.81'),
