(1844, 'Bianca Bucur', 'ANYbotics AG', 'bbucur@anybotics.com', '41443051130', 'ANYbotics AG', 'Zürich', '24sqm', '15,000 EUR', '1', 'Dear Sirs,\r\nWe will be exhibiting at SPRINT World Conference in Antwerp at the end of October with a floor space of 24sqm. Attached you have our standard design which hopefully will help you to create an offer for us. The budget is purely for orientation. If you need more details about the design, please reach out to me via email. I do not own a company mobile number therefore I am easier to reach via email.\r\n\r\nThank you!\r\nBest,\r\nBianca Bucur', '/stand-design-and-booth-construction-company/brussels/', '2024-03-25 22:43:05', '2024-03-25 22:43:05', '213.3.24.157'),
(1845, 'Bianca', 'Balmain Hair', 'bianca.v@balmainhair.com', '31643165342', 'Cannes Festival', 'Cannes', NULL, NULL, '3', 'Hello, \r\nMy name is Bianca from the Balmain Hair PR team and I am reaching out regarding a glam hub during the Cannes Film Festival.\r\nWe would like to create 4 make-up stands (NARS) and 4 hair stands (Balmain Hair); see the floor plan attached for how we\r\nimagine this. We need this for the period of 13-26 May.\r\n4x HAIR STANDS:\r\n- Tables\r\nWhite matte/ shiny \r\nHeight 32 inches approx.\r\nWidth 45 inches approx. \r\nDepth 15 inches approx. \r\n- Chairs \r\nStandard salon chairs \r\n37-43 inches height approx. \r\nWith logo ( see image attached from last year)\r\n- Mirrors \r\nPreferably white with lights incorporated \r\nPart of the table \r\nWith brand logo (see image attached from last year)\r\n4x MAKE-UP STANDS:\r\n- Tables\r\nBlack - matte/ shiny ok (maybe they have options)\r\nHeight 44 inches approx.\r\nWidth 33 inches approx (or longer?)\r\nDepth 23 inches approx.\r\n- Chairs \r\nStandard plain black director chairs\r\n- Mirrors\r\nPreferably black / plain\r\nHollywood Mirrors\r\nIn the bathroom, we are creating a small studio for video recordings. Here we would need one director chair also.\r\nI would like to hear if the above is possible, and could you send me a quotation, please? \r\nDo not hesitate to contact me if you have any questions.\r\nBest,\r\nBianca', '/stand-design-and-booth-construction-company/cannes/', '2024-03-26 17:26:17', '2024-03-26 17:26:17', '185.127.184.118'),
