(1855, 'Bethany Bolton', 'iFi Audio', 'bethanyb@ifi-audio.com', '07939685491', 'High end munich', NULL, '30SQMT', NULL, '2', 'Hello! We need a booth for the High End Munich Show May 2024. Our booth is 5m x 6m and joined on 2 sides to other booths.\r\n\r\nOur graphics team are still drawing up the plan, so we will be able to get that to you on Tuesday.\r\n\r\nour theme is a traditional museum, showcasing the history of our products and our brand.\r\n\r\nWe would like marble effect floor, coving, pillars to stand at the 3 open corners of the booth, a 1m storage disguised behind the 5m back wall, and floor standing white plinths for our products to stand on.\r\n\r\nthese plinths will be hollow with holes at the top to allow power cables to pass from our products, through the plinth, and through back walls, into power cables on the other side, making everything completely seamless.\r\n\r\nWe also will provide frames that are 6cm deep to put on the wall. We would like the 6m wall to be brought forward by 10cm, and the deep frames to be recessed into both walls, Making it look seamless to the viewer. The 10cm gap behind the 6m wall will Also allow for power on that side.', '/contact-us/', '2024-03-29 03:06:13', '2024-03-29 03:06:13', '82.7.46.164'),
