(1871, 'Miki Oakley', 'Biocatalysts Ltd', 'miki.oakley@biocatalysts.com', '01443843712', 'FiE', 'Cardiff', '6mx9m', '35000', '', 'I am reaching out to discuss the possibility of working with you for a tradeshow we are exhibiting at this year. FiE at Messe Frankfurt. \r\nWe are on booth 3.1L20 and have a 6mx9m booth space.\r\n\r\nWe are looking for two meeting rooms, one room to fit a table and at least 4 chairs, and the other to fit a table and at least 6 chairs. We would like a reception area, which can also display some collateral, and potentially an area for coffees. It would be great to have three or four meeting tables on the booth, with potentially one or two of these being high tables, something to create height or a high level hanging display, and a large LED screen, and a smaller screen. \r\nLast year we found an issue with people walking across the booth from the open sides, so we would like to mitigate this issue this year.\r\n\r\nI look forward to hearing from you.', '/fi-europe-and-hi/', '2024-04-04 18:25:22', '2024-04-04 18:25:22', '83.219.46.14'),
