(1876, 'Mohammad Hassino', 'MixJet', 'marketing@mixjet.aero', '971544325334', 'EBACE24', 'Geneva, Switzerland.', '108 square meters', '70,000$', '1', 'Dear Sir/Madam,\r\nI trust this message finds you in good health.\r\nI am reaching out to communicate the specifications and requirements for the upcoming design project.\r\nPrimarily, we aim to embrace a dynamic design concept reminiscent of the successful design displayed at last year\'s MEBAA show. Please refer to the attached design for reference. The focus should lie on integrating organic shapes while minimizing the use of straight lines.\r\nIn terms of the color palette, our primary colors revolve around golden tones, as illustrated in our attached logo guidelines.\r\nFurthermore, we express a preference for a matte black flooring with a single wheelchair ramp. We propose the inclusion of natural and wooden elements to underscore our dedication to sustainability.\r\nRegarding seating arrangements, as nine delegates are expected to attend the show, we require sufficient meeting spaces. This encompasses one large round table, one designated sofa area, and two seating zones each accommodating four chairs and a small table.\r\nMoreover, we would appreciate your innovative touch in creating a seating area encircling a central tree within the stand, aligning it harmoniously with our brand identity.\r\nFor the outdoor side, we seek a sleek and uncomplicated outdoor presentation. \r\nAdditionally, we recommend the incorporation of large screens to enhance visual engagement and request the installation of a bar counter.\r\nPlease be advised that our budget is approximately $45,000, and time is of the essence. If you could deliver the design proposal by Friday, we would greatly appreciate it.\r\nThank you for your attention to these specifications.', '/ebace/', '2024-04-08 15:08:03', '2024-04-08 15:08:03', '82.137.250.13'),
