(1889, 'Anne Roeder', 'Michelangelo International Travel srl', 'anne.roeder@michelangelo-travel.com', '390464571261', 'World Travel Market', 'Riva del Garda', '18 sqm (6*3)', NULL, '1', 'Hello from Italy,\r\nafter years of booking a shell sheme package, we are now considering a personalized stand design for our stand at WTM this November. Our stand has two open sides (with a wall on the left-hand side; the right-hand side is right next to the entrance). We also need a small store room and our main objective is to create more space within our rather small stand. I attach a photo of our 2023 stand for you to get an idea of our status quo. \r\nPlease send an offer and some design examples.\r\nKind regards,\r\nAnne Roeder', '/world-travel-market/', '2024-04-12 16:42:17', '2024-04-12 16:42:17', '84.18.151.50'),
(1890, 'Alper Gulek', 'IVF Prime', 'alper.gulek@ivfprime.com', '905304434704', 'ESHRE 2024 Annual Meeting', 'Amsterdam', '18m2', '5K-10K Euro', '2', 'Hello,\r\nI am writing to you from IVF Prime. We are participating in ESHRE 2024 which will be held in RAI Amsterdam this July.\r\nWe are in search of a stand contractor company for the congress. Our booth will be 18m2 and attached, I am sharing some photos of our booth last year (same size). We would like to keep the design but also be open to some recommendations as well.\r\nLooking forward to hearing from you soon.', '/stand-design-and-booth-construction-company/amsterdam/', '2024-04-13 12:53:18', '2024-04-13 12:53:18', '212.91.241.58'),
(1891, 'Madeleine Allardice', 'Archivist', 'madeleine@archivistgallery.com', '01608658601', 'Maision & Object', 'Paris', '3m x 6m', NULL, '1', 'The photo is from our stand at last years show. This September we would like you to make us 3m tall walls along two sides, that are white and are solid (so we can screw into them). We we also need you to install and take down the walls, thank you so much, yours Madeleine', '/stand-design-and-booth-construction-company/paris/', '2024-04-15 20:42:34', '2024-04-15 20:42:34', '86.138.231.17'),
(1892, 'Alessandra Vinck', 'Opera', 'avinck@opera.com', '662221567', 'DMEXCO', 'Barcelona', '40-50sqm', '25000', '', 'Hi there! \r\nWe will be exhibiting at this year\'s DMEXCO 2024 on 18 + 19 September in Cologne, Germany and are looking for a stand builder. We have applied for a 40sqm 2 corner stand but at the end of April/beginning of May we will hear if we can get a bigger booth (up to 50 sqm) and if we can get a 3 corner space. \r\n\r\nRequirements: \r\n- Storage space\r\n- Welcome desk \r\n- Coffee corner/Bar area \r\n- A minimum of 4 meeting spaces (We can have 2 more private rooms for previously booked meetings and 1 open space with standing tables/lounge area. \r\n- Opera Ads branding and Opera logo on top. \r\n\r\nWe will be participating with Opera Ads, the advertising platform by Opera. Opera Ads fuels monetization and effective user engagement through a comprehensive suite of products including a demand-side platform (DSP), supply-side platform (SSP), and Premium Ad Solutions.\r\nThe purpose of the exhibition participation: build awareness and have an effective meeting space (last year our booth was fully booked at all times) \r\nTarget group: B2B ad tech companies, advertisers, publishers, DSP\'s and SSP\'s. \r\nBudget: 25K \r\nThe appearance of the stand: modern, sleek design. Last year\'s booth here: blogs.opera.com/ads/2023/09/opera-ads-dmexco\r\n\r\nLooking forward to hear more about your company and if we could potentially work together. \r\n\r\nBest, \r\nAlessandra', '/stand-design-and-booth-construction-company/cologne/', '2024-04-15 20:58:51', '2024-04-15 20:58:51', '79.154.14.0'),
