(1906, 'Pernille Friis', 's.e.w. north filtration', 'pmf@northfiltration.com', '23231063', 'Filtech 2024', 'Cologne', '7x4 m', '6700', '1', 'We are interested in collaborating with you to create a trade show booth for our participation at Filtech. We have attached a file with a concept booth, which we would like you to use as a reference when preparing a proposal for us.\r\nWe have some specific requirements for the new booth that we hope you can assist us in fulfilling:\r\n\r\n1.	A tall wall/pillar to make our logo visible from a distance to attract attention.\r\n2.	A storage room with lockable doors. Inside, there should be space for a mini fridge and a coat hanger.\r\n3.	A reception desk along with two stools or a bar table with stools.\r\n4.	A small lounge area with armchairs and a coffee table.\r\n5.	Space for displaying filters and other materials.\r\n6.	Printed materials for the back walls.\r\n\r\nWe would appreciate it if you could provide us with a proposal based on these requirements, including any additional suggestions or ideas you may have to enhance the booth\'s effectiveness at the event', '/stand-design-and-booth-construction-company/cologne/', '2024-04-22 18:00:22', '2024-04-22 18:00:22', '80.208.28.106'),
