(1930, 'PENSUDA LERTJATUPHORNCHAI', 'SMS Corporation Company Limited', 'pensuda@smscor.com', '025981128', 'Food Ingredients Europe (Fi Europe) 2024', NULL, '34.95SQMT', NULL, '1', 'I hope this message finds you well. \r\nAllow me to introduce my company: SMS Corporation is a global leader in manufacturing modified tapioca starch for food and nonfood industries.\r\nSMS is participating in the Food Ingredients Europe (Fi Europe) 2024, scheduled to take place from November 19 – 21 at Frankfurt, Germany.  We would like to invite you to partner with us for the design and construction of our exhibition booth.\r\nWe are confident that your expertise in booth design and construction will help us create an engaging and visually appealing space that effectively represents our brand and attracts visitors to our booth.\r\nFurthermore, we attached a file of our previous booth for your inspiration.\r\nIf you are interested in collaborating with us, we would like to share our requirements in more detail and hear your ideas for the booth design.\r\nWe look forward to the possibility of working with you.', '/contact-us/', '2024-04-29 12:35:29', '2024-04-29 12:35:29', '183.88.232.151'),
(1931, 'Mark Edwards', 'TTi', 'mark.edwards@aimtti.com', '01480412451', 'Electronica 2024', 'Huntingdon, Cambridgeshire', '6m x 3m', '€10k', '1', 'This is a our fist own both at a show in Europe. We want more than a  shell scheme  presentation but have a tight budget. The attached image shows our most recent  shared booth at Electronica and the  suggested   rental  stand. We are expecting to get confirmation of our both space in the next week.', '/modular-exhibition-stands/', '2024-04-29 16:21:28', '2024-04-29 16:21:28', '217.155.53.150'),
