(1986, 'Zlata Aleynikova', 'Mujin Netherlands B.V.', 'zlata.aleynikova@mujin.co.jp', '31630303309', 'LogiMat 2025 Stuttgart', NULL, '400SQMT', NULL, '1', 'Dear Sirs,\r\n\r\nI hope this email finds you well. My name is Zlata and I am a marketing/PR specialist representing Mujin Netherlands B.V. based at Eindhoven, NL. We would like to exhibit at LogiMat 2025 at Stuttgart and showcasing our latest innovation.\r\n\r\nWe are looking for a help with a booth planning, design and execution, and other additional services. \r\n\r\nWe are currently in discussions regarding the type of solution we would like to present at LogiMat 2025. As part of our deliberations, we are considering a booth size of approximately 400 square meters with an end stand configuration (3 sides open). We will know more details once our application will be accepted. \r\n\r\nIs it possible to get an estimate like do you provide such service, how is your team will be working with us, what will be an estimate procing, etc.? Could you provide a detailed list of the services you offer related to booth design and setup?\r\n\r\nI appreciate your assistance in this matter and look forward to receiving your response. If you have any questions or require further information, please do not hesitate to contact me  at zlata.aleynikova@mujin.co.jp \r\n\r\nSincerely,\r\nZlata \r\n\r\nAbout Mujin:\r\n\r\nMujin, a robotics technology company, develops “machine intelligent” robot controllers that are designed as a common platform for industrial and collaborative robots specializing in logistics and manufacturing applications. Launched in Tokyo in 2011 with offices in China, U.S. and Europe (opened in 2023), Mujin works with many of the world’s largest companies to make material handling applications easier to deploy, more accurate and less costly. \r\n\r\nOur flagship product, MujinController, uses machine intelligence technology (MujinMI) to give robotic systems real-time decision-making ability that enables truly autonomous, reliable, and production-capable robot applications. MujinMI controls multi-axis machines and enables smarter applications with multiple degrees of freedom, empowering robots to move with precision and flexibility.', '/contact-us/', '2024-05-14 09:06:43', '2024-05-14 09:06:43', '39.110.214.243'),
(1987, 'Sujittra', 'Samadoon', 'sujittra@samadoon.co.th', '0619146561', 'Sports Authority of Thailand', 'Thailand', 'TBC', 'TBC', '', 'Hello, I am contacting from Thailand. My team is interested in coming to a booth at your event.\r\nPlease send me the information.', '/iftm/', '2024-05-14 14:42:33', '2024-05-14 14:42:33', '58.136.151.62'),
(1988, 'Ilaria Zaccariello', 'Inventronics Srl', 'ilaria.zaccariello@inventronicsglobal.com', '393208878144', 'LiGHT24', 'Treviso', '12 sqm', '18000', '1', 'Dear,\r\n\r\nI am Ilaria Zaccariello, marketing team from Inventornics Italy (former OSRAM DS). We are a lighting components manufacturer, producing flexible and rigid LED modules, LED drivers and connectivity systems for lighting.\r\n\r\n\r\nWe are looking for a new UK based partner for trade show booths realization, that can support us this year and also in the future. I am contacting you after checking your website and portfolio: I am sure that your really professional expertise could be exactly what we are looking for.\r\n\r\nFor the time being, I am writing you because we are currently looking for a booth contractor that can follow us for the stand realization and installation for the LiGHT24 event in London, 20 – 21 November. \r\nWe will have a 3 x 4 m booth (12sqm).\r\n\r\n \r\nWe already have a design idea, where we should install some of our products. You can see the design proposal in the attached file.\r\n\r\nBecause of internal processes, we would need to have the final design ready possibly at the end of may, maximum by the end of the first week of June. This will allow us to produce and order all the products that we would like to show/install at the fair.\r\nOur budget for the realization and the installation would ideally be max 18.000 £ (VAT excl.). - Please consider that all the lighting products and drivers can be provided by us (only the LED modules for the optional backlit logo might be discussed, it depends on the dimensions), and we can support during the installation of them on site.\r\n\r\nDo you think you can support us for this event, given the indicated budget?\r\n\r\nIn case, we could also have a video call to discuss the project.\r\n\r\nLet me know. Thank you!', '/custom-exhibition-stands/', '2024-05-15 14:08:40', '2024-05-15 14:08:40', '93.34.144.117'),
