(2038, 'Sameh Najjar', 'SELT', 'mkg@seltmc.com', '0021692661052', 'SELT', 'Frankfurt', '66.5', 'less than 50000', '', 'We would like to request two separate quotes (rental and purchase) for the design, construction, assembly, and disassembly of a stand for the FIE EXPO 2024, which will be held in Frankfurt from November 19 to 21, 2024.\r\nStand area: 66.5 m²\r\nRequested services:\r\nAssembly and disassembly of the stand and stand management\r\nGraphic design, simulation, and preparation of all documents required by the FIE2024 platform regarding design and assembly\r\n2 reception desks with chairs\r\n2 high tables with chairs\r\nVIP area (armchairs with a coffee table)\r\nLight boxes\r\nGiant screen (3.75 m)\r\nPlants\r\nBrochure holders\r\nLighting (spotlights and ceiling lights)\r\nPrinting', '/stand-design-and-booth-construction-company/frankfurt/', '2024-05-28 20:19:47', '2024-05-28 20:19:47', '41.226.165.57'),
