(2043, 'Arti Sharma', 'NaturMed Scientific', 'arti.sharma@naturmedscientific.com', '8448354526', 'FI Europe', 'Frankfurt', '9m2', NULL, '1', 'We have an upcoming exhibition in November FIE Europe. Could you let us know if you can help with this and share the quote with us.\r\n\r\nThis is our booth number 3.0A68 of 9m2. \r\n\r\nWe need the following: \r\n\r\n1.	3mx3m walls and this we would need posters accordingly. \r\na.	Two posters 3m each \r\nb.	Or 6 individual posters of size 100cmx 250 cm posters to be printed for exhibitions. \r\nWe have the design and can share with you to print the posters that can stick directly on the WALL ELEMENTS mentioned below.\r\nFloorplan Fi Europe 2024 Frankfurt – please have a look and let me know if you have any questions.', '/fi-europe-and-hi/', '2024-05-29 12:09:45', '2024-05-29 12:09:45', '122.162.148.49'),
(2044, 'Tom Wood', 'Agriline Products', 'tomwood@agrilineproducts.com', '01527579111', 'Agriline Products', 'Bromsgrove', '32m2', '£6,000', '4', 'Hello,\r\nWe are looking to attend EIMA 2024 but are trying to understand the total costs associated with exhibiting before paying out deposit to the organizers.\r\nI have attached image of a stand that was completed by one of our competitors that we like the look of. The display cases, the open space with seating so that we can sit down and entertain customers, storage room for bags and merchandise that is lockable over night. \r\nWe would also require an area that we can either set up a laptop or have a reasonable sized screen to show our distributor websites.\r\nWe do not want a raise floor, or the hanging banner from the ceiling as we know this will add significant cost.', '/eima-international/', '2024-05-29 14:38:54', '2024-05-29 14:38:54', '51.155.83.2'),
(2045, 'Seungman Seo', 'M3mobile GmbH', 'ssm@m3mobile.net', '4961929222153', 'parcel post expo', NULL, '6*6mSQMT', NULL, '', 'Hallo,\r\n\r\nwir möchten uns nach einem Stand für die Messe im Oktober in Amsterdam und im März in Düsseldorf nächsten Jahres erkundigen. Die Standgröße beträgt 6x6m. Da wir Hersteller von PDA-Geräten, also ähnlichen Smartphones sind, benötigen wir eine Ausstellungsfläche für unsere Produkte & Tische und paar Stühle, einen kleinen Lagerraum und ein hangenden Banner an der Decke. Könnten Sie uns diesbezüglich ein Angebot unterbreiten?\r\n\r\nWir freuen uns auf Ihre Antwort. Vielen Dank.', '/contact-us/', '2024-05-29 16:56:11', '2024-05-29 16:56:11', '37.24.243.130'),
(2046, 'Nixon', 'Insight Electronic', 'nixonkch22@gmail.com', '07432834446', 'Electronica', 'Munich', '42 Square meter', NULL, '', 'Hello,\r\nThis is Insight Electronic Ltd., we are a PCB manufacturer from Taiwan. We are looking for exhibition stall design/ decoration. We are attending the Electronica 2024 in Munich from 12th November to 15th November, and we will be attending every two years. Our stand this year is 42 square meters. I am here to inquire if  Triumfo had work on similar project before. We are expecting a booth that provides a sense of technology, and futuristic impression. Besides, our company would also prefer blue and white as the main colour. Is there any project that Triumfo  had done before that I can have as a reference, or perhaps we can arrange a meeting and discuss. \r\nBest,\r\nNixon', '/modular-exhibition-stands/', '2024-05-29 20:48:52', '2024-05-29 20:48:52', '137.22.174.33'),
(2047, 'Eva Jančíková', 'MALINA - Safety s.r.o.', 'eva.jancikova.jr@malina-safey.cz', '420601207541', 'Expoprotection 2024', 'Paris', '7x7', NULL, '3', 'Good morning,\r\nI am writing to ask you to prepare a visualization and a quotation for the EXPOPROTECTION 2024 stand.\r\nAttached is a visualization of the booth we had in 2022, as well as the hall plan for this year. \r\nWe have a surface area of 7x7 m. \r\n \r\nHere\'s what we\'ll need for the stand:\r\n•        Two or three meeting tables, each with four chairs.\r\n•        Small reception area.\r\n•        A compact utility room\r\n•        One mannequin dummy on a pedestal – requiring an electricity connection from the pedestal at 110V-230V.\r\n•        For product presentations, we plan to use a \"slat wall\" system, \r\nOur primary color scheme consists of red, white, and black/grey. For further inspiration, please visit our website at Clean Air Website\r\n \r\nIf you need any further information, please don\'t hesitate to contact me.\r\n \r\nHave a nice day 😊', '/expo-protection/', '2024-05-30 12:39:20', '2024-05-30 12:39:20', '85.119.88.70'),
