(2050, 'Marianne CONFAIS', 'NOVACEL SAS', 'mconfais@novacel-solutions.com', '0670822655', 'GLASSTEC', 'Düsseldorf', '30', NULL, '', 'Hello, \r\nWe are an industrial international company based (headquarter based in France). We are specialized in process and protective films for various materials (glass, stainless steel, plastics...) since 40 years. \r\nWe organize a number of international trade shows every year. I\'m in charge of organizing European trade shows for the company. \r\nWe are participating at Glasstec trade show coming up in October, for our glass market. \r\nWe\'ve been working with a stand creator for years and are now looking for a new serious, efficient and responsible partner. We\'re currently interviewing several. I\'d like to talk to you about our stand project and get a price quote. Can you contact me please? \r\nBest regards. \r\nMarianne CONFAIS', '/stand-design-and-booth-construction-company/dusseldorf/', '2024-05-31 14:55:17', '2024-05-31 14:55:17', '88.138.129.131'),
