(2175, 'Jimmy', 'Irvine Agency', 'mjimmy4@hotmail.com', '00201124909090', 'Caffex', 'Lost angeles', '12x6x3', 'Not determined', '2', 'am writing to request your assistance in producing a booth for an upcoming event at The Los Angeles Nestle from Egypt will be showcasing some of their brands, including Nescafe, Nestle Paradise Ice Cream, Kitkat, and Maggi, at this event. The products will be shipped from Egypt, and we need the following for the booth production:\r\n\r\n1. **Booth Production Requirements**:\r\n\r\n   - **Flooring**: HDF floors, wood floors, or PVC – whichever is cheaper and more convenient. The shades and colors should match as closely as possible to the presentation attached.\r\n\r\n   - **Acrylic LED Logo Signages**: For the four brands.\r\n   - **Booth Shape**: Rectangular, with dimensions of 16 meters by 12 meters.\r\n\r\n   - **Booth Height**: Must not exceed 3 meters.\r\n\r\n   - **Furniture**: Two glass low tables with three chairs each, and two high tables with four chairs each.\r\n\r\n   - **Materials for Walls, Columns, and Shelves**: Any available material, but should closely match the colors in the presentation.\r\n\r\n2. **Additional Information**:\r\n\r\n   - The machines to be placed inside the booth are still under negotiation, so we are uncertain if we will require them from your side, as well as the ushers.\r\n\r\n   - The event will take place from July 26 to August 4, and we can start setting up from July 22.\r\n\r\nCould you please provide a price list for the requested items and confirm whether it is possible to produce them? Additionally, please let us know how long the production will take.\r\n\r\nPlease find the presentation attached for your reference.\r\n\r\nWe appreciate your prompt response and look forward to working with you on this project.\r\n\r\nBest regards,', '/stand-design-and-booth-construction-company/los-angeles/', '2024-06-30 05:30:46', '2024-06-30 05:30:46', '197.52.70.129'),
