(2179, 'Jessica Jones', 'Incident Zero', 'jessica@incident-zero.com', '61459361153', 'MINExpo International', 'Las vegas', '10x20\'', NULL, '1', 'Hello,\r\nWe are looking for a stand builder to quote our stand build for MINExpo happening in September in Las Vegas. \r\nWe are located in the North Hall, Booth 3167 – 20’x10’. The goods need to be delivered to the GES warehouse prior to Sept 11 for delivery on Sunday 22nd September which installation can then start on this day. \r\nI have attached a mock up if you have a booth design similar to this that you could quote and include our requirements below would be amazing.\r\nAlso as the timing is getting tight please let me know your deadline, we are based in Australia so we are also working in different time zones from one another.\r\nRequirements\r\n-	Full black walls with logo in white and blue line around the bottom of the wall\r\n-	Option of 65” & 85” TV for the back wall\r\n-	TV’s on the cabinet/s - need to be something we can access our website on to show customers during the show, probably around a 32”\r\n-	Excavator will be rented from a dealer in Vegas\r\nIf you can send a quote and a stand mock up for our executive team to review it would be appreciated, if you need anything further to proceed with this please let me know.', '/minexpo-international/', '2024-07-02 16:44:37', '2024-07-02 16:44:37', '122.150.156.197'),
