(2240, 'Kristina Kim', 'BauWatch', 'kkim@bauwatch.com', '31659354521', 'SAIE', 'Bologna', '40 sq m, 3 open sides', '----', '4', 'Dear team,\r\nI hope this message finds you well. \r\nMy name is Kristina, Country Marketing Manager at BauWatch. We are preparing for the SAIE fair that will take place in Bologna, from 9-12 of October, and looking for a supplier for the BauWatch stand. \r\nPlease kindly find the requirements for the stand below:\r\n•	The stand is 40 sq m. 5m*8m, 3 opened sides. Please find the floor plan attached, stand # B15. \r\n•	Carpet anthracite \r\n•	1 pc. Ceiling cube, (ceiling suspension required), with foil cut-outs.\r\n•	1 high wall 3 m high\r\n•	Small lockable cabin with\r\no	Washbasin (water connection and raised floor min. 8 cm, as well as a ramp prescribed by the trade fair)\r\no	Refrigerator\r\no	Clothes hooks\r\no	Coffee corner\r\no	1 shelf for storing goods and personal items.\r\n•	2 bar table with 4 bar stools\r\n•	1 pc. Meeting table with 4 chairs\r\n•	2 pcs. Counter cabinets \r\n•	2 monitors \r\n•	Planter boxes for visual separation, 90-100cm high\r\n•	Planning, production, packaging, transport, assembly and dismantling. \r\n•	We bring 2 video surveillance towers to exhibition. They require a place of approx. 1.10 x 1.10 m and are approx. 6 m high when fully extended (Forklift truck required).\r\nWe will provide all graphic print files for film cuts or wall prints which is needed. However, the layout of the stand, production would have to be carried out by you. Please find the preliminary designs that we used for other fairs as inspiration. \r\n\r\nCould you please make a rough, non-binding offer with price for production and very simple design layout? Please let me know if we can schedule an introductory call to discuss details. \r\n\r\nThank you and have a great start of the week.\r\n\r\nKind regards,\r\nKristina', '/stand-builders-italy/', '2024-07-23 15:20:42', '2024-07-23 15:20:42', '185.27.17.210'),
