(2390, 'Hande', 'Van Gestel', 'hyilmaz@estro.org', '32471611367', 'ESTRO 2025', 'Vienna', '500 sqm', NULL, '', 'I hope this message finds you well. I am contacting you on behalf of the European Society for Radiotherapy and Oncology (ESTRO). We are organizing our annual congress, ESTRO 2025, which will be held at the Vienna Messe Congress from May 2-6, 2025, and are seeking an exhibition contractor to provide shell scheme booth services for the event.\r\nEvent Details:\r\n•	Event Name: ESTRO 2025 Annual Congress\r\n•	Venue: Vienna Messe Congress\r\n•	Dates: May 2-6, 2025\r\n•	Total Exhibition Space: 4,500 sqm\r\n•	Total Event Space (including catering and lounge areas): 10,000 sqm\r\n•	Number of Exhibitors: Approximately 100 (with 40-50 exhibitors requiring shell schemes)\r\nBuild-up Schedule:\r\n•	Monday, April 28: 08:00-22:00 (early build-up for booths = or >100 sqm)\r\n•	Tuesday, April 29: 08:00-22:00\r\n•	Wednesday, April 30: 08:00-22:00\r\n•	Thursday, May 1: 08:00-22:00\r\n•	Friday, May 2: 08:00-12:00 (Booth construction completed by 12:00; packaging to be removed)\r\nExhibition Opening Hours:\r\n•	Friday, May 2: 18:00-20:00\r\n•	Saturday, May 3: 09:30-17:00\r\n•	Sunday, May 4: 09:30-17:00\r\n•	Monday, May 5: 09:30-17:00\r\nBreak-down Schedule:\r\n•	Monday, May 5: 17:00-00:00\r\n•	Tuesday, May 6: 08:00-22:00\r\n•	Wednesday, May 7: 08:00-22:00\r\nServices Required:\r\nWe are seeking an estimate for providing shell scheme booths for approximately 40-50 exhibitors. The estimate should cover the following:\r\n1.	Shell scheme booth construction\r\n2.	Delivery and setup based on the build-up timeline above\r\n3.	Breakdown and removal after the event\r\n4.	Additional services such as booth customizations, lighting, furniture, or signage (if available)\r\n5.	Terms of service or conditions we should be aware of\r\nCould you kindly provide us with a pricing estimate for the services mentioned above? Additionally, please include any relevant details regarding timelines and other available services that could enhance the event.\r\nThank you for your time and consideration. We look forward to your proposal and are happy to provide any further details if necessary.', '/stand-design-and-booth-construction-company/vienna/', '2024-09-17 14:43:05', '2024-09-17 14:43:05', '178.51.107.213'),
