(2604, 'ERDINC TAN', 'K2 EVENTS', 'erdinc.tan@k2-events.com', '+905332823662', 'ASUS ELEVATE SUMMIT', 'BOLOGNA, ITALY', NULL, NULL, '', 'Dear  sirs,\r\n\r\nI hope this message finds you well. My name is Erdinc TAN, and I am the Managing Partner at K2 Events Istanbul. One of our clients, ASUS, is planning to host a summit in Bologna, Italy, on February 24-25, 2025. While the hotel has not yet been confirmed, the event itself will take place on February 25, 2025.\r\n\r\nAs part of the event, ASUS intends to create a DEMO ZONE for their visiting partners. We have developed several design concepts, which I would like to share with you through the following link. \r\nhttps://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1dVg5ti2m_yBOP6wUPadfIoxDmfvGKyNT?usp=sharing\r\nWe are reaching out to inquire about your interest in providing the requested services, and if possible, to request a budget proposal for the construction of the DEMO ZONE.\r\n\r\nOur design team has made every effort to include all relevant details in the attached documents. However, should you require any additional information, please feel free to contact us at your convenience.\r\n\r\nWe are planning to book the meeting venue on February 24, 2025, one day prior to the event, to allow for the setup of the DEMO ZONE. Based on your professional experience, could you kindly advise if a single setup day would be sufficient for the attached DEMO ZONE?\r\n\r\nWe greatly appreciate your interest and cooperation, and we look forward to your response at your earliest convenience.\r\n\r\nBest regards,\r\nErdinc TAN (erdinc.tan@k2-events.com)\r\nManaging Partner | K2 Events Istanbul', '/stand-design-and-booth-construction-company/bologna/', '2024-11-14 15:09:54', '2024-11-14 15:09:54', '87.200.146.182'),
(2605, 'Amy Lewis', 'Music Tribe', 'amy.lewis@musictribe.com', '074848883981', 'NAMM', 'Bedford', '40X50', NULL, '', 'We are exhibiting at the NAMM show, Anaheim CA, Jan 23-25 2025.\r\nWe need a booth as follows:\r\n\r\n40 x 50ft\r\nDouble decker - two meeting rooms upstairs\r\n(Upstairs does not need to be the whole floor space)\r\nDisplay downstairs to host 4 walk-through zones, incorporating 9 audio and music equipment brands\r\nOne brand will take up approx half the space, with the other eight sharing the remainder\r\nFluid, versatile space with plenty of counters for product display\r\nFull graphic package, lighting etc.\r\nWe need the full service - build, take-down, labor etc.\r\n\r\nWe are looking to keep costs down for this, so open to suggestions as to the most economical way to build this while still making it look modern and classy.\r\n\r\nDo you have capacity, and could you provide an approximate estimate given the tight timeline?', '/stand-design-and-booth-construction-company/anaheim/', '2024-11-14 19:07:10', '2024-11-14 19:07:10', '151.229.8.188'),
