(2668, 'Sara Wang', 'SAPER PTE.LTD', 'sifan.wang@sapergroup.com', '+86 18942405049', 'Kingpins', 'Amsterdam', NULL, NULL, '', 'Dear Triumfo,\r\nI am writing on behalf of SAPER PTE. LTD., a leading Chinese company specializing in denim fabric dyes. We are extremely interested in participating in the Kingpins Show to be held in Amsterdam in 2025.\r\nOur company has been committed to providing high-quality and innovative denim dyes, which have been widely recognized and praised in the industry.  We believe that participating in this prestigious event will not only help us showcase our latest products and technologies but also provide an excellent opportunity to network with industry leaders and potential customers.\r\n\r\nWe would like to reserve a booth at the show.  Could you help to provide us with the necessary information on booth availability, pricing, and reservation procedures?  We are looking forward to a successful cooperation and a great event.\r\n\r\nFor more information about our company, please refer to https://www.sapergroup.com/saper\r\nThank you very much for your attention and assistance.\r\n\r\nBest regards,\r\nSara Wang\r\nGeneral Manager Assistant', '/kingpins-show/', '2024-12-02 08:10:44', '2024-12-02 08:10:44', '120.235.91.131'),
(2669, 'Karthick ps', 'Kumar organic products limited', 'kopdigitalmarketing@kumarorganic.net', '8553927217', 'INCOSMETICS GLOBAL', 'Amsterdam, Netherlands', '66 sqm', NULL, '', '1.	What is your company ethos?\r\nKumar Organic Products Limited stands for innovation, sustainability, and quality as a leading manufacturer of active ingredients. We focus on delivering solutions that enhance health and well-being while promoting environmentally friendly practices.\r\n2.	How do you want to present yourself at the show?\r\nWe want to position ourselves as a trusted active ingredient manufacturer, with a strong focus on bioferments promotion and our commitment to sustainable innovation in the personal care and pharmaceutical industries.\r\n3.	Do you want to design a sustainable stand?\r\nYes, we prefer a sustainable stand that aligns with our company’s ethos of environmentally responsible practices.\r\n4.	Which products will be promoted by you? – Will provide you shortly\r\n5.	Do you have any specific design in mind?\r\nWe would like a modern, clean, and engaging design that highlights our products prominently, with ample branding space to showcase our active ingredients and bioferments. The stand should feel inviting and innovative, with eco-friendly elements.\r\n6.	What is your furniture requirement?\r\n•	Reception counter\r\n•	Product display shelves or units ( Highlighted)\r\n•	Meeting tables and chairs (for 15 - 20 people)\r\n•	Storage space for brochures and other materials\r\n•	TV\r\n•	Storage room\r\n7.	Do you require rigging?\r\nYes, we would require rigging for overhead branding to ensure visibility from a distance.', '/in-cosmetics/', '2024-12-02 13:54:15', '2024-12-02 13:54:15', '72.14.201.139'),
