(2694, 'Salman Hanif Khan', 'info@hansamfg.com', 'info@hansamfg.com', '03466611555', 'AIMS', NULL, '10-10SQMT', NULL, '', 'Dear Concern\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nGreetings.\r\n\r\nI hope this email finds you well.please note the below requirements for our booth at the upcoming AIM Expo 2025. Also our budget is under $4000 to $5000.\r\n\r\nOur booth number is #5116. The booth size is 10x10 feet, and we would like to request your assistance in providing the following items and services for our display: \r\n\r\nBooth Requirements:\r\n1.       10\'x8\' back wall with two side walls\r\n\r\n2.       Multiple rows of hooks on the rear half wall for displaying 30 pairs of assorted gloves\r\n\r\n3.       Shelves on the rear half wall to display our boots (8-10 feet of assorted boots)\r\n\r\n4.       Custom printed graphics for branding and visual display\r\n\r\n5.       Reception counter with storage and our logo\r\n\r\n6.       15 hand mannequins for displaying gloves (Picture is attached)\r\n\r\n7.       Electric socket at the meeting table for power\r\n\r\n8.       20 coat hangers to display our leather and textile jackets\r\n\r\n9.       125 cm hook shelves on one side of the booth\r\n\r\n10.   4 LED arm lights for booth illumination\r\n\r\n11.   Table with 2 stools for interaction with visitors\r\n\r\nAdditionally, we will be displaying:\r\n\r\n· 30 pairs of assorted gloves\r\n\r\n· 8-10 feet of assorted boots\r\n\r\n· 20 pieces of leather and textile jackets\r\n\r\nCould you kindly provide a detailed quote for the requested items and services, including the cost of delivery, setup, and removal? Also, please let us know if you require any further details to prepare an accurate estimate.\r\n\r\nWe look forward to your response and hope to establish a long-term collaboration for this event and future projects.\r\n\r\nThanks\r\n\r\nArshad', '/contact-us/', '2024-12-06 19:23:14', '2024-12-06 19:23:14', '39.61.57.114'),
