(2767, 'Irina', 'Science Education Group', 'imischenko@yandex.ru', '+79112345468', 'SILMO 2025', 'Paris, Istanbul', '/', NULL, '', 'Dear Organizers of the International Conference,\r\n \r\nWe express our sincere interest in participating in your event and would like to offer our support as an information sponsor. We are confident that our expertise and resources will help attract additional attention to the conference and its key topics.\r\n \r\nOur company (www.se-group.pro) encompasses several areas (the main website is still under development): additional professional education for ophthalmologists and optometrists - MADO Academy www.dpo-spb.ru, a scientific and educational portal Optometry Online www.optometriaonline.ru (currently only available with auto-translation into other languages), a residency program in Ophthalmology, and clinical research aimed at stabilizing myopia in children.\r\n \r\nWe would like to present a report dedicated to current issues regarding the stabilization of myopia in children or topics related to optometry, with a special emphasis on working with children. We believe this topic is of great interest to the professional community and requires further discussion. We also wish to initiate the creation of a new section dedicated to optometry. We are ready to take on the organization of this section to ensure its high scientific and practical level. Special attention in the section will be given to pediatric optometry, which we believe is a crucial area for the development of the industry.\r\n \r\nWe would appreciate the opportunity to discuss the details of our potential collaboration. Thank you for considering our proposal, and we hope for fruitful cooperation.\r\n \r\nSincerely,\r\n \r\nIrina Emelyanova\r\nCEO\r\nSe-group\r\n+7-911-234-54-68\r\nnok@se-group.pro', '/silmo/', '2025-01-03 20:33:36', '2025-01-03 20:33:36', '5.18.179.17'),
