(2773, 'Gucsi-Végh Ivett', 'Print Brokers Team Kft', 'nyomdaonline025@printbrokers.hu', '06703412553', 'Christmas World', 'Győr - HUNGARY', '4 nm', NULL, '', 'Dear Triumfo,\r\nWe are a printing and packaging technology company, and we are interested in learning more about your exhibition. We have not participated in the past, but we are curious about the details to determine whether it would be worthwhile for us to attend.\r\nCould you please provide more information about the event? Specifically:\r\nWhat type of exhibitors typically participate?\r\nWhat is the profile of the majority of the visitors?\r\nHow long has the exhibition been organized?\r\nHow have participant numbers evolved over the past three years?\r\nAdditionally, I would like to ask the following:\r\n\r\nAre there any special sections or workshops during the event?\r\nIs there an opportunity for exhibitors to hold presentations during the exhibition?\r\nWhat promotional opportunities are available for exhibitors (e.g., inclusion in the exhibition catalog or online)?\r\nHow do you support exhibitors in connecting with visitors (e.g., networking events, matchmaking programs)?\r\nFinally, could you kindly send us a quote for exhibition stands of 4, 6, and 8 square meters? We would appreciate it if you could include details about what is included in the price.\r\n\r\nThank you very much for your assistance. I look forward to your reply.\r\nBest regards,\r\nIvett Gucsi-Végh - marketing manager\r\nPrint Brokers Team Ltd\r\nhttps://printbrokersteam.hu/home', '/christmasworld/', '2025-01-06 16:56:52', '2025-01-06 16:56:52', '185.5.231.50'),
