(2847, 'Peter Pastinsky', 'Cruiser Aircraft', 'pastinskypeter@gmail.com', '+421944477057', 'AERO Friedrichshafen 2025', 'Friedrichshafen', '10x20', NULL, '', 'Hello, we are going to be attending AERO Friedrichshafen 2025 and exploring potential partners to assist with construction design and cons.\r\n\r\nWe represent Cruiser Aircraft, and at this year’s expo, we will be exhibiting three aircraft within our booth. We are looking for a high-quality, innovative, and functional booth design that effectively showcases our aircraft while providing an engaging experience for visitors.\r\n\r\nBooth Specifications:\r\nSize: 10m x 20m\r\nRequirements:\r\nSpace to exhibit three aircraft\r\nA welcoming reception area\r\nBranding and signage integration\r\nLounge or meeting space for discussions\r\nLighting and audiovisual elements for an engaging presentation\r\nWe would appreciate it if you could provide:\r\n\r\nA quotation for the booth design, construction, installation, and dismantling.\r\nInitial design ideas or previous examples of similar exhibition stands you have worked on.\r\nDetails on your process, timeline, and any logistical considerations for Messe Friedrichshafen.\r\nPlease let us know if you require any additional information to provide an accurate quote. We look forward to your response and the opportunity to collaborate.\r\n\r\nThank you,\r\nPastinsky', '/exhibition-stand-contractors-builder-in-friedrichshafen/', '2025-01-22 17:57:59', '2025-01-22 17:57:59', '178.41.196.198'),
