(2918, 'Tatiana', 'Kondratieva', 'tatiana.kondratieva@exely.com', '+172641612367', 'Exely', 'Berlin', '28', NULL, '7', 'Dear Triumfo Company,\r\nWe would like to ask you for the service of building a stand for the ITB-2025 exhibition for our company 😊\r\nFirst of all, this year our stand is twice as big as last year (the plan is attached)\r\nWe have a concept and we would like to focus on it when building the stand. \r\nWe have created a 3D model of the furniture arrangement at our stand, so I hope this will make your task much easier (see the attachment to the letter) \r\n\r\nThis year we are focusing on the topic of space, but not directly, but only indirectly. \r\nI\'ve attached a reference of the stand, but please don\'t take it literally, we just want to convey the atmosphere. \r\n\r\nMoreover, we would like to place a photo zone on one of the walls.\r\nCan you tell me what options you can offer? I\'ve also attached references to the letter that you can use.\r\nMaybe a purple foil background and something like light bulbs or garlands to make it look more interesting (but I also want it to be neat and not get out too much) \r\n\r\nWe would also very much like you to offer us various options of the ceiling design. \r\nLast year, we made a hanging LED screen, and it really attracted the attention of the guests.\r\nCan we also do something high above our heads this time so that it stops the gaze of passing people? \r\nMaybe you can suggest some options suitable for our theme, or something luminous that can also attract visitors? \r\n\r\nOur budget (including all additional details in the Beco Shop) is approximately $16,000\r\nAlso, the exhibition is in a month and we would like to receive any possible offers asap.\r\nI will attach various references, among others, and I will be happy to answer any of your questions. \r\n\r\nI am looking forward to your reply., \r\nThank you in advance!', '/', '2025-02-06 16:22:40', '2025-02-06 16:22:40', '213.194.98.62'),
