(2924, 'Miguel García Díaz', 'Innerspec Technologies Europe S.L.', 'mgdiaz@innerspec.com', '911337024', 'Control 2025', 'Loeches, Madrid', '6m x 3m', NULL, '', 'We are Innerspec Technologies Europe, an NDT manufacturer offering both integrated and portable solutions for various industries. You can find information about our company on our website: www.innerspec.com\r\n\r\nOur booth number is #7200 in Hall 7, measuring 6m x 3m, with two open sides.\r\n\r\nWe require a stand with a small storage room (1.5m x 1m) positioned in the closed corner. Additionally, we would like to include graphics on the back wall, covering all the wall. We will design the graphics and provide the files.\r\n\r\nFor furnishings, we need:\r\nA counter cabinet with a lockable door at the front, where we will conduct product demonstrations on top.\r\nA high table with 3–4 stools or high chairs. (we don\'t want to cover much space, as we will place a 1.2m long pipe in the middle of the stand to conduct demonstrations)\r\nAt the last edition, our ROI for this event was relatively low, so we want to keep the budget contained. For reference, in the proposal, please avoid including elements like hanging lights that require rigging or complex structures that might increase costs. A simple and clean design should be sufficient. \r\nDon\'t hesitate to reach out if you have any questions.', '/control/', '2025-02-07 18:32:35', '2025-02-07 18:32:35', '80.32.54.138'),
