(2932, 'Karthikeyan Gandhi', 'Premier Fine Linens', 'karthikeyang@premiermills.com', '+91-8220299333', 'Heimtextil', 'Frankfurt', '100 sq.m', NULL, '', 'I represent Premier Fine Linens Pvt Ltd, a leading manufacturer of high-quality linens and textiles. We have been participating in the Heimtextil – Messe Frankfurt show for several years and are currently looking for a reliable vendor to handle the design and construction of our exhibition stall for the upcoming event.\r\n \r\nWe would appreciate it if you could provide us with the following details:\r\n \r\n•	Portfolio: Images and videos of stalls you have designed and constructed, preferably textile or home textile industry.\r\n•	Services: A list of services you offer, including design, construction, installation, and dismantling.\r\n•	Price Quotes: A detailed quotation for stall construction, including any additional costs for materials, lighting, graphics, or other customizations.\r\n•	Timeline: Estimated timelines for design approval, construction, and installation.\r\n \r\nWe would also like to know if you offer post-event dismantling and storage services.\r\n \r\nPlease let us know if you need any additional information from our side to provide a proposal', '/heimtextil/', '2025-02-11 14:19:01', '2025-02-11 14:19:01', '42.104.112.34'),
