(2944, 'Rafael Diniz', 'Digicon SA', 'rafael.diniz@digicon.com.br', '5551998661745', 'PTX - Passenger Terminal Expo', 'Madrid', '36', NULL, '', 'Digicon will be at the PTX show in Madrid that goes from April 8-10. Build up starts in April 6th.\r\nWe\'ll have a 36sqm booth (#1431) with 2 open sides.\r\nSpecs are:\r\n•	4m high walls (or as high as the show allows) fully covered in graphics to be provided by us. It should be able to support a 60 inches TV (TV will be provided by us, we only need a back plate to attach it);\r\n•	Small counter with 2 doors to store backpacks and some catalogues – maybe around 60 centimeters deep x 120 centimeters wide and 100 centimeters high approx;\r\n•	3 high stools;\r\n•	Platform with ramp OR padding + carpet in light grey color (we want to evaluate pricing on both options)\r\n•	Lights – this is very important. Our CEO is very sensitive about it, we must have powerful light in our booth;\r\n•	Power to the booth and 5 sockets (1 for TV, 1 for counter and 3 for equipment we\'ll display).\r\n \r\nOptionally rigging rounded sigh with our logo on it (this may be expensive so I’m not sure we’d do it).\r\ntks', '/stand-design-and-booth-construction-company/madrid/', '2025-02-12 20:14:09', '2025-02-12 20:14:09', '200.182.168.150'),
