(2947, 'Isa Larsson', 'Malina', 'isa.larsson@bymalina.com', '0735353134', 'Paris fashion week', 'Stockholm', NULL, NULL, '3', 'Hi,\r\nIn March, 5-11th, we will have our own showroom at Rue Charlot in Paris. For that, we need a paper wall, or exhibition stand builder. It will stand by itself, no one will see the background.\r\n Size; 200 cm wide x 224 cm high x around 20 cm width (you can help us with the width measurement, it’s important that it can stand up by it’s own)\r\n We want to check offer two types of form.\r\n 1. 200 cm wide x 224 cm high, x 20 xm width flat\r\n2. 200 cm wide x 224 cm high, x 20 xm width, with arch\r\nEither way we want the whole wall to be printed or in a plain colour.\r\nIs this something you can do?\r\nThank you!', '/stand-builders-france/', '2025-02-13 16:00:32', '2025-02-13 16:00:32', '79.142.251.115'),
