(3032, 'Kiley Bennett', 'Bonnie Christine', 'kiley@bonniechristine.com', '2704050291', 'Licensing Expo', 'Las Vegas', '20x30', NULL, '', 'Hi there,\r\nI hope you\'re doing well! My name is Kiley Bennett, and I’m reaching out on behalf of Bonnie Christine, a leading surface pattern\r\ndesigner and licensing brand. We are excited to be exhibiting at the Licensing Expo in Las Vegas on May 20-22 and are looking for a booth builder to help bring our vision to life.\r\nWe have a 600 sq. ft. booth space and have worked with a draftsman to create an initial draft of our dream booth. Now, we’re seeking a partner to refine the design, build, and fully set up our booth inside the expo hall. Since we were a late addition to the show, we understand that a 2-month turnaround may be tight based on your process, but we hope that the pre-work we’ve done will help streamline the build and keep things moving quickly.\r\nWould you be available to discuss feasibility, timelines, and next steps? Looking forward to hearing your thoughts\r\nBest,\r\nKiley Bennett\r\nDirector of Licensing + Representation\r\nBonnie Christine (https://www.bonniechristine.com/)', '/stand-design-and-booth-construction-company/las-vegas/', '2025-03-12 09:50:18', '2025-03-12 09:50:18', '75.88.87.127');
