(3062, 'Maria', 'Perfect Pavers of South Florida', 'leonid3053220016@gmail.com', '7547326551', 'Perfect Pavers of South Florida', 'Palm beach Miami', NULL, NULL, '', 'Good afternoon,\r\n\r\nMy name is Maria, and I represent Perfect Pavers of South Florida. We specialize in professional paver installation and are considering participating in the Home Show. Since we have no prior experience with such events, we would like to gather as much information as possible to prepare effectively.\r\n\r\nWe would appreciate it if you could provide details on the following questions:\r\n\r\nParticipation Process: What are the main steps to becoming an exhibitor? Is there a selection process?\r\nCosts: What is the cost of participation? Are there different booth options, and what factors influence pricing?\r\nBooth Size: What booth sizes do companies in our industry typically choose? Which formats are most popular among exhibitors?\r\nBooth Design: Who is responsible for designing the booth? Do you have recommended designers or companies we could consult?\r\nCompetitors: Which companies from our industry usually participate? What strategies do they use to stand out?\r\nEffective Engagement Strategies: What elements tend to attract the most visitors (e.g., live demonstrations, interactive areas, giveaways)?\r\nDeadlines and Timelines: What are the key dates we need to be aware of? When should we submit our application, approve the booth design, and complete all preparations?\r\nEquipment and Inclusions: What is included in the standard exhibitor package? Do we need to bring our own equipment, or are certain items provided by the organizers?\r\nMarketing and Promotion: Does the event offer any promotional opportunities for exhibitors (e.g., catalogs, newsletters, social media features)?\r\nLogistics and Setup: How does material delivery and booth setup work? Are there any safety or time restrictions for installation?\r\nAdditional Costs: Are there any hidden or extra fees, such as for electricity, water, or internet access?\r\nWe want to fully understand the process so we can prepare efficiently and make the most of this opportunity. We would greatly appreciate any information or advice you can provide to help us make an informed decision.\r\n\r\nThank you for your time — we look forward to your response!', '/miami-home-design-and-remodeling-show/', '2025-03-20 00:14:22', '2025-03-20 00:14:22', '143.107.88.11'),
